{"type":"message","id":"c896119e","parentId":"b521a3ee","timestamp":"2026-03-28T09:17:22.141Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. I've successfully completed the autonomous learning task. Let me provide a brief summary of what was done.","thinkingSignature":"821ec830fa5b3c54e36956e83c2bb723284ecacccfc4f1639f0598c5884addda"},{"type":"text","text":"**自主学习已完成** ✅\n\n无活跃对话，执行了完整的自主学习流程：\n\n1. **搜索了3个核心领域**（企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成+IT运维）\n2. **整理了5条关键信息**，覆盖：\n   - 数字化转型政策红利（工业数据筑基行动、专项补贴）\n   - 智能安防市场高速增长（2026年中国规模超2000亿元）\n   - AI原生网络与Agentic AIOps转型趋势\n   - IT运维从成本中心向价值中心转型\n   - 传统运维模式淘汰警示\n3. **已保存至** `memory/学习笔记.md`，包含道简网络业务针对性启示\n\n**下次自动更新**：2周后（2026-04-11）"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4973,"output":184,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49138,"cost":{"input":0.0014919,"output":0.0002208,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00303213}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774689436786}}
